StringLiteralExpr.value: Polynomial order (n) must be an integer.
Differentiation order (dn) must be an integer.
The Polynomial Order must be less than the frame length.
The Differentiation order must be less than or equal to the Polynomial order.
The weight vector must be real.
The weight vector must be of the same length as the frame length.
All the elements of the weight vector must be greater than zero.
